<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Skyview Ranch</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A breathtaking neighborhood with idyllic landscapes, immaculate greens and panoramic views of the surrounding Rockies, the community in Skyview Ranch is a perfect place to start a family or spend a tranquil and relaxing life post-retirement.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">The well established Skyview Ranch Real estate offers its residents peace and quiet along with a dynamic suburban lifestyle that makes life in the community, easy-going.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Recreational opportunities abound in the area with the Village Square Leisure Center, the YMCA Bishop McNally and the Don Hartman North East Sportsplex located within its close proximity.</p>
        </div>
